"ry'ukoresha \" > Imizi < /> Ijambobanga ikoresha A &GUI; Ikiganiro , I Kuri "
"Birenzeho Bya A command Umurongo: &lt; - &gt; &GUI; Bya A &GUI; Porogaramu . "

